Virtusize,is,a,virtual,fitting,platform,that,helps,users,to,find,the,right,size,and,fit,for,clothing,on,eCommerce,and,retail,websites,Virtusize,helps,shoppers,by,overlaying,garments,silhouettes,to,find,the,right,size,The,Virtusize,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Virtusize,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,measurements,and,sizes,returning,images,and,managing,product,details